reviews.text: One of the best Soymilk abs Tofu pudding in Hong Kong!   Bad service is part of the experience.

Bad services and attitude to customers , very meanmean to people in all possible ways . It's not the only tofu shop in the area, and it's not the best . I wanted to order a bowl of hot tofu pudding, but they don't have it.  I almost walked out after I got humiliated, and wanted to start the argument after another customer got humiliated also
Taste is good but crowded. But this is famous.
Very nice bean curb pudding and you can have a bowl of it after touring in Kowloon City
A tradition soy bean cafe in HK,you can experience a high quality soy product here.Dark soy milk and some rare vegetarian snack  sold here. Open at afternoon

reviews.text: 冇禮貌，串到爆！
態度惡劣不友善，出品遜於公和，衞生形象麻麻。14:00仍未有熱花供應，即是只有隔夜凍的
好多款式，三寶有4款！
煎釀三寶大件抵吃👍
豆腐花很滑 不似有太多石膏 黃糖內裏加了白沙糖 白沙糖是死甜 要減分 因為等朋友 才吃下兩碗 ＄9 有點貴 可一不會再
